abstract: Those looking to see swift movement and fluid quality from Sevilla and Atletico Madrid on Sunday night were mostly out of luck.
snippet: Those looking to see swift movement and fluid quality from Sevilla and Atletico Madrid on Sunday night were mostly out of luck.
lead_paragraph: MADRID -- Two teams with Champions League aspirations and a referee and part-time sociologist from Pamplona stepped on to the field at the Vicente Calderón stadium on Sunday evening.

headline.main: Inside a Boiling Calderón: Atlético Madrid and Sevilla Draw, 0-0
